          <image class='star-red-25' src="http://www.huachengzhubao.com/syweb10/static/ico/star.png"></image>
          <image class='star-red-25' src="http://www.huachengzhubao.com/syweb10/static/ico/star.png"></image>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class='comment-conent'>从前初识这世间,万般流连,看着天边似在眼前,也甘愿赴汤蹈火去走它一遍,如今走过这世间,万般流连,翻过岁月不同侧脸,措不及防闯入你的笑颜</view>

  </view>

